  "title": "제주도 비자림 단풍",
  "addDate": "2013. 11. 26.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110180348560",
  "html_size": 190227,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110180348560\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110180348560\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&#65279;일정이 있어서 제주도에 갔다가, </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">짧은 시간을 쪼개서 비자림을 다녀왔습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">11월 말인데, 지금이 단풍 절정이더군요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">비자림을 자주 가는 편인데,&nbsp;갈때마다&nbsp;항상 짙푸른 녹색 숲만&nbsp;봤었죠.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">이번에 단풍을 보게 되서 너무나 신기했네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">단풍이 너~무 예뻐요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_160/isuhani_1385428506019KC85v_JPEG/IMG_5367.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_160/isuhani_1385428506019KC85v_JPEG/IMG_5367.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_160/isuhani_1385428506019KC85v_JPEG/IMG_5367.JPG?type=w3\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">주차장에서 본 비자림의 입구입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_53/isuhani_1385428573378N9N8r_JPEG/IMG_5368.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_53/isuhani_1385428573378N9N8r_JPEG/IMG_5368.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_53/isuhani_1385428573378N9N8r_JPEG/IMG_5368.JPG?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">입구에 매점과 조그만 카페도 있어요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">카페 이름이 '비자림' ^^</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">입구의 나무들만 봐도 아주 오래된 숲의 느낌이 납니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_153/isuhani_1385428666047W45Aq_JPEG/IMG_5274.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_153/isuhani_1385428666047W45Aq_JPEG/IMG_5274.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_153/isuhani_1385428666047W45Aq_JPEG/IMG_5274.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">비자림 진입로의 소공원</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_150/isuhani_1385428666381fAtPl_JPEG/IMG_5278.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_150/isuhani_1385428666381fAtPl_JPEG/IMG_5278.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_150/isuhani_1385428666381fAtPl_JPEG/IMG_5278.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">진입로. 이 길의 끝에서 비자림이 시작됩니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_182/isuhani_138542920004119bdv_JPEG/IMG_5332%281%29.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20131126_182/isuhani_138542920004119bdv_JPEG/IMG_5332%281%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_182/isuhani_138542920004119bdv_JPEG/IMG_5332%281%29.jpg?type=w3\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">단풍나무의 크기가 범상치 않습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">이렇게 큰 단풍나무는 처음 봤네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_96/isuhani_1385429270423g3gaw_JPEG/IMG_5299.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_96/isuhani_1385429270423g3gaw_JPEG/IMG_5299.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_96/isuhani_1385429270423g3gaw_JPEG/IMG_5299.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">11월 말의 추위에도 단풍은 선명한 노란색을 보여주고 있네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">서울은 은행잎이 다 떨어지고 있는데 말이죠. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_27/isuhani_1385429270862T7v49_JPEG/IMG_5305.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_27/isuhani_1385429270862T7v49_JPEG/IMG_5305.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_27/isuhani_1385429270862T7v49_JPEG/IMG_5305.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>숲이 울창해서 밝은 낮인데도 </p>\r\n<p>숲속은 어둑어둑 합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_185/isuhani_1385429271239YdjPY_JPEG/IMG_5319.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_185/isuhani_1385429271239YdjPY_JPEG/IMG_5319.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_185/isuhani_1385429271239YdjPY_JPEG/IMG_5319.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>짙푸른 비자나무 숲 사이사이 노랗고 붉은 단풍들이 </p>\r\n<p>매력적입니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_237/isuhani_1385429271551H4BDr_JPEG/IMG_5364.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_237/isuhani_1385429271551H4BDr_JPEG/IMG_5364.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_237/isuhani_1385429271551H4BDr_JPEG/IMG_5364.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">높은 나무 꼭대기의 단풍잎들도 불에 타 오르듯 한 껏 붉은 기운을 내뿜고 있더군요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">시간이 촉박하지 않았다면 한참을 앉아있다 오고 싶었습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">다시 찾은 비자림에서 뜻밖의 단풍을 만나서 너무나 행복했습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">오는길에. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">제주도까지 갔는데 바닷가를 가보지 못한 아쉬움을 달래느라</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">차를 잠시 세워두고 바다를 한 컷 담았습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_264/isuhani_1385433095532tGVjk_JPEG/IMG_5257.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20131126_264/isuhani_1385433095532tGVjk_JPEG/IMG_5257.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A742B290')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131126_264/isuhani_1385433095532tGVjk_JPEG/IMG_5257.JPG?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">커플룩을 입은 한쌍의 연인이 바닷가의 경치를 더욱 아름답게 해주더군요 ^^</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
